---

<BaseLayout title="Astro Islands Demo" description="Interactive components showcasing writing portfolio capabilities.">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-slate-100 dark:from-slate-900 dark:to-slate-800">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 space-y-16">
      
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <section class="text-center py-16">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          Astro Islands in Action
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Experience the power of Astro Islands with these interactive components designed to showcase writing work, 
          engage visitors, and demonstrate expertise through dynamic, client-side interactivity.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Interactive Writing Showcase -->
      <section class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">Interactive Writing Showcase</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Filter, search, and explore writing samples with real-time interactivity. This component demonstrates 
          how Astro Islands can create engaging portfolio experiences.
        </p>
        <InteractiveWritingShowcase writingSamples={writingSamples} />
      </section>

      <!-- Dynamic Content Preview -->
      <section class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">Dynamic Content Preview</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Interactive content previews with expandable sections, metrics display, and smooth animations. 
          Perfect for showcasing article excerpts and case study highlights.
        </p>
        <DynamicContentPreview content={sampleContent} />
      </section>

      <!-- Client Testimonial Carousel -->
      <section class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">Client Testimonial Carousel</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Smooth, interactive carousel showcasing client testimonials with autoplay, touch/swipe support, 
          and keyboard navigation. Builds trust and credibility.
        </p>
        <ClientTestimonialCarousel testimonials={sampleTestimonials} />
      </section>

      <!-- Writing Process Timeline -->
      <section class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">Interactive Writing Process Timeline</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Step-by-step process visualization with expandable details, progress tracking, and interactive elements. 
          Demonstrates methodology and builds confidence in your approach.
        </p>
        <WritingProcessTimeline processSteps={processSteps} />
      </section>

      <!-- Interactive Reading Experience Demo -->
      <section class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">Interactive Reading Experience</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Enhanced article reading with progress tracking, table of contents, highlight mode, and share functionality. 
          Creates an engaging, professional reading experience.
        </p>
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <InteractiveReadingExperience 
            article={{
              title: "The Future of Content Marketing: AI, Personalization, and Authenticity",
              content: `
                <h2>Introduction</h2>
                <p>The content marketing landscape is evolving rapidly, driven by advances in artificial intelligence, 
                changing consumer expectations, and the need for more personalized, authentic experiences.</p>
                
                <h2>The AI Revolution in Content</h2>
                <p>Artificial intelligence is transforming how we create, distribute, and optimize content. From 
                automated content generation to predictive analytics, AI tools are becoming indispensable for 
                modern content marketers.</p>
                
                <h3>Content Generation at Scale</h3>
                <p>AI-powered writing tools can now generate high-quality content at unprecedented scale, but 
                the human touch remains irreplaceable for strategy, creativity, and emotional connection.</p>
                
                <h2>Personalization Beyond Demographics</h2>
                <p>True personalization goes beyond basic demographic targeting. It requires understanding 
                individual preferences, behaviors, and contextual needs to deliver relevant content at the 
                right moment.</p>
                
                <h2>Authenticity in the Digital Age</h2>
                <p>As AI-generated content becomes more prevalent, authenticity becomes a competitive advantage. 
                Brands that maintain genuine human voice and transparent communication will stand out.</p>
              `,
              readingTime: "8 min read",
              wordCount: 850,
              publishedDate: "2024-01-20T00:00:00Z",
              tags: ["Content Marketing", "AI", "Personalization", "Future Trends"]
            }}
          />
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Benefits Section -->
      <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Why Use Astro Islands for Your Writing Portfolio?</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">🚀 Performance</h3>
            <p>Only load JavaScript where needed, keeping your site fast and SEO-friendly while adding interactivity where it matters most.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">💡 Engagement</h3>
            <p>Interactive components keep visitors engaged longer, increasing the likelihood they'll explore your work and contact you.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">📊 Analytics</h3>
            <p>Track user interactions with your portfolio components to understand what content resonates most with potential clients.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">🎨 Flexibility</h3>
            <p>Mix static and interactive content seamlessly, using islands only where they add genuine value to the user experience.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">🔧 Maintainable</h3>
            <p>Each island is self-contained, making it easy to update, test, and maintain individual components without affecting the rest of your site.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">📱 Responsive</h3>
            <p>All components are built mobile-first with touch support, ensuring a great experience across all devices and interaction methods.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
